    "name": "Bird Simulator 24",
    "steam_appid": 3262870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take flight in <i>Bird Simulator 24</i>, an outrageous action game where you reclaim your rightful territory from the humans and assert your genetic dominance! As a fearless bird, your mission is simple: rule the skies, reclaim your homeland, and fight the humans in the most hilarious ways imaginable.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can you restore peace to the park?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the plot of the corrupt mayor scheming to demolish it, and fight to protect the greenery in all-new story mode missions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/d3045850e9ddc18a2d874bb0cd279fa4.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/d3045850e9ddc18a2d874bb0cd279fa4.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Eat Anything You See!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge and devour everything that crosses your path! Every bite helps you rack up points and trigger special power-ups. The more you eat, the more chaos you can unleash!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/63aff8c42d4f3e48d814270a9f44680e.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/63aff8c42d4f3e48d814270a9f44680e.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Skins and Hats!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization is key to showing off your birdly style! Collect and unlock dozens of unique skins and hats for your bird.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/cc6285c460851ef561f53a95085bc0bc.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/cc6285c460851ef561f53a95085bc0bc.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash Birdly Vengeance on Humans!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use anything in the environment to your advantage—trash cans, benches, cardboard boxes, and even ice cream stalls! Various edible items can come in handy providing a variety of combat effects, such as fireworks or donut immunity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/bbdf19fd7c77e4edb70840cc2fba01f0.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/bbdf19fd7c77e4edb70840cc2fba01f0.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Poop with Precision!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate weapon in your arsenal: poop! Aim carefully as you dive-bomb targets from the sky. Time your shots perfectly to hit unsuspecting humans and cause maximum chaos. Precision pooping has never been more fun—or deadly.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/5c0b057c4e13e471cb7f726770b0feed.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/5c0b057c4e13e471cb7f726770b0feed.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover Hidden Secrets in a World Full of Surprises!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a world filled with quirky secrets and hidden areas. Can you uncover all secrets?  Only the most cunning and adventurous birds will find them all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras/be6d4c61ad7ef3723108b1b5dc45d4a2.avif?t=1759130680\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262870/extras_big/be6d4c61ad7ef3723108b1b5dc45d4a2.avif?t=1759130680 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to reclaim the skies and become the ultimate bird overlord?</strong></p>",
